Description: # Django Tools Blog
        
        Django app to add blog to your website
        
        ## Installation
        
        1. Install with pip install `django-tools-blog`.
        
        2. Add `djtools.blog` to your INSTALLED_APPS setting like this:
        ```
        INSTALLED_APPS = [
            ...
            'djtools.blog',
        ]
        ```
        
